{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, PLUTO was trained on millions of image patches, and incorporating diverse data sources such as genomic information, significantly enhances performance in tasks like cancer detection and molecular prediction (31).",
    "These models not only enhance diagnostic precision but also reduce the time and resources required for model development, paving the way for expanded clinical applications.",
    "However, the availability of these large pathology models is currently limited mostly to academic publications, and many are not yet open-sourced.",
    "Lu and colleagues presented PathChat, a vision-language generalist AI assistant for human pathology.",
    "In comparison tests, PathChat outperformed GPT-4 with 26.4% improvement on the open-ended questions and more specialization in pathology (32)."
  ]
}